error.name: NOT_AUTHORIZED
error.description: Method requires authentication and a user is not logged in.

error.name: NO_EFFECTIVE_USER
error.description: Root user does not call sudo before calling method with flag S.

error.name: NO_PERMISSION
error.description: User does not have permissions to access the calendar.

error.name: COMPONENT_EXISTS
error.description: Calendar object already exists in the calendar.

error.name: UNKNOWN_COMPONENT
error.description: Calendar object was not found in the calendar.

error.name: INVALID_QUERY
error.description: Given query function does not exist or is not implemented.

error.name: READ_ONLY
error.description: Read-only backend is used for users, groups etc. (e.g. LDAP)

error.name: DOMAIN_VIOLATION
error.description: Foreign domain violated. (e.g. user from different domain tried to create.)

error.name: SPF_VIOLATION
error.description: SP method violates DNS TXT record.

error.name: NOT_MEMBER
error.description: User is not member of group.

error.name: UNKNOWN_METHOD
error.description: Method does not exist or is not implemented.

error.name: INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR
error.description: Server error. (DB failures, disk full conditions, etc.)

error.name: CLIENT_ERROR
error.description: Client error. (Errors caused by caller not covered by another error code)
